      "title": "Suspended postal services resume",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Postal Department announced that accepting postal shipments to the US, Netherlands and Israel, which had been suspended have resumed today.",
        "Postmaster General Ranjith Ariyaratne said the postal shipment services were restricted due to fuel crisis. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
